lead_paragraph: Adidas has agreed to expand its partnership with Kanye West, including opening new stores, hoping to build on its higher profile in the U.S. market since it poached the singer-turned-designer from Nike in 2013.

headline.main: Adidas Strikes New Deal With Kanye West in U.S. Market Push
